@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
title Contoso University Integration Component Diagram
component "ApprenticeshipsContext" as ApprenticeshipsContext
component "AwardsContext" as AwardsContext
component "CoursesContext" as CoursesContext
component "PaymentsContext" as PaymentsContext
component "StaffContext" as StaffContext
component "StudentsContext" as StudentsContext
CoursesContext --> StudentsContext : Azure Service Bus
PaymentsContext --> StudentsContext : Azure Service Bus
StudentsContext --> AwardsContext : Azure Event Grid
CoursesContext --> AwardsContext : Azure Event Grid
CoursesContext --> ApprenticeshipsContext : Azure Service Bus
StudentsContext --> ApprenticeshipsContext : Azure Service Bus
PaymentsContext --> ApprenticeshipsContext : Azure Service Bus
PaymentsContext --> StaffContext : Azure Integration Services
CoursesContext --> StaffContext : Azure Integration Services
@enduml
